marketing: Shell Spirax S6 TFVM is a premium quality, top-tier Universal Tractor Transmission Oil (UTTO) designed to provide superior performance in Fendt Vario as well as other agricultural equipment applications. The improved wear protection performance supported by enhanced shear stability can help to reduce unplanned downtime and to prolong equipment and component lifetime.
